Tirada dadka si deg deg ah ugu xanuunsanaya cudurka faafa ee coronavirus (COVID-19) ee Midowga Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Ingiriiska intii u dhaxeysay 1-dii Janaayo ilaa 15-kii Maarso 2020.
Cudurka isugu jira ee cudurka coronavirus (COVID-19) wuxuu leeyahay isbeddel la mid ah wadamada Midowga Yurub/Aagga Dhaqaalaha Yurub iyo UK, taas oo xaqiijineysa in inkastoo heerarka kala duwan ee uu ku jiro wadamada kala duwan, masiibada COVID-19 ay si deg deg ah ugu sii kordheyso dhammaan wadamada.
Marka la eego khibrada Talyaaniga, dalalka, isbitaalada iyo qaybaha daryeelka degdegga ah waxay u baahan yihiin inay sare u qaadaan diyaar garowga bukaannada COVID-19 ee u baahan daaweyn iyo gaar ahaan daryeelka degdegga ah.
31kii Diseembar 2019 magaalada Wuhan ee gobolka Hubei ee Shiinaha waxaa laga diiwaangeliyey dhowr kiis oo ah cudurka sambabada oo aan la garanayn sababta.
Bishii Janaayo 9, 2020, Xarunta Xakamaynta iyo Ka Hortagga Cudurrada ee Shiinaha ayaa sheegtay in cudurka uu sababay nooc cusub oo ah coronavirus, oo hadda loo yaqaan coronavirus oo ah nooca 2aad ee cudurka neefsashada ee daran (SARS-CoV-2).
Laga soo bilaabo xilligaas, cudurka SARS-CoV-2 waxaa loo yaqaan cudurka coronavirus (COVID-19).
Sida laga soo xigtay xogta la heli karo ilaa maanta, qiyaastii 80% dadka qaba COVID-19 waxay qabaan cudur fudud, taas oo ah infekshan neefta oo leh ama aan lahayn sambabada, dadka badankoodna way bogsadaan.
Qiyaastii 14 boqolkiiba kiisaska COVID-19 waxay u gudbaan xaalad daran oo u baahan in la dhigo isbitaalka, halka 6 boqolkiiba kalena ay noqdaan kuwo daran oo u baahan daaweyn degdeg ah.
Heerka dhimashada bukaanka la dhigay isbitaalka COVID-19 waa qiyaastii 4%.
Daraasaddan ayaa lagu falanqeeyay isbeddellada cudurka COVID-19 ee ku soo kordha waddan kasta oo ka tirsan Midowga Yurub (EU) / Aagga Dhaqaalaha Yurub (EEA) iyo UK, waxaana la barbar dhigay isbeddellada gobolka Hubei ee Shiinaha.
Waxaan sidoo kale isbarbar dhigeynaa tirada hadda ee COVID-19 ee Midowga Yurub/Aagga Dhaqaalaha Yurub iyo UK iyo tirada Talyaaniga ee laga helay 31 Janaayo ilaa 15 Maarso 2020.
Xaaladaha COVID-19 ee Midowga Yurub/Aagga Dhaqaalaha Yurub iyo UK
COVID-19 ayaa ka faafay dalal kale ka dib markii uu ka dillaacay Shiinaha, waxaana hadda caalamka intiisa kale uu ku socdo masiibada COVID-19 oo la mid ah tii Shiinaha.
11-kii Maarso 2020, Agaasimaha Guud ee Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka (WHO) ayaa ku dhawaaqay cudurka faafa ee COVID-19.
Sawirka 5 March 2020 ee Eurosurveillance, Mr Spiteri iyo asxaabtiisu waxay soo sheegeen kiisaskii ugu horreeyay ee la xaqiijiyay ee COVID-19 ee Yurub oo buuxiyay shuruudaha WHO ee lagu ogaado jiritaanka cudurka.
Saddexda kiis ee ugu horeeyay ee la xaqiijiyay ee Midowga Yurub/EEA ayaa laga helay Faransiiska 24kii Janaayo 2020  Saddexda qof ee la xaqiijiyay waxay ka soo laabteen magaalada Wuhan ee gobolka Hubei ee Shiinaha.
Laga soo bilaabo 15-kii Maarso 2020, dhammaan 30-ka dal ee Midowga Yurub/EEZ iyo UK waxaa laga helay COVID-19, iyadoo laga soo bilaabo 31-kii Diseembar 2019 ilaa taariikhdaas la diiwaangeliyey 39 768 xaaladood oo cudur ah iyo 1 727 dhimasho, kuwaas oo 17 750 kiis, oo ay ku jiraan 1 441 dhimasho ah, ay ka dhaceen Talyaaniga oo keliya.
Qeexida tirada isku darka ah iyo cudurka isku darka ah ee COVID-19
Xarunta Xakamaynta iyo Ka Hortagga Cudurrada Yurub (ECDC) ayaa maalin kasta 8:00 subaxnimo cusbooneysiineysa xogta ku saabsan tirada kiisaska COVID-19 ee laga helay waddan kasta oo adduunka ah, oo laga helay ilo rasmi ah sida wasaaradaha caafimaadka ee wadamadaas, maamulada caafimaadka ee qaranka iyo kuwa gobolka iyo WHO.
Xogtan waxaa loo isticmaalaa in lagu falanqeeyo isbeddellada faafitaanka COVID-19 ee Midowga Yurub/Aagga Dhaqaalaha Yurub iyo UK loona barbardhigo xogta Talyaaniga.
Heerka faafitaanka kiisaska firfircoon ee COVID-19 waxaa loo xisaabiyay 14 maalmood oo la soo koobay oo ah COVID-19 oo lagu qiyaasay heerka caadiga ah ee COVID-19 ee waddan kasta oo Midowga Yurub/EEZ ah iyo UK intii u dhaxaysay 1-dii Janaayo ilaa 15-kii Maarso 2020.
Waxaan sidoo kale soo bandhignay tirada guud ee kiisaska laga helay waddan kasta saacaddii 8:00 subaxnimo ee 15-ka Maarso 2020, marka la barbar dhigo tirada laga helay Talyaaniga intii u dhaxeysay 31-kii Janaayo iyo 15-kii Maarso 2020.
Isbeddellada COVID-19 ee wadamada Midowga Yurub/EEZ iyo UK
Isbeddellada cudurka COVID-19 ee la isku daray ee 14-ka maalmood ee EU/EEA iyo UK guud ahaan waxay la mid yihiin isbeddellada laga arkay gobolka Hubei ee Shiinaha (Sawir 1).
Tirada dadka qaba COVID-19 ee ku soo uruursan EU/EEA iyo UK guud ahaan waxay bilaabeen inay koraan qiyaastii 21 Febraayo, waxaana kor u kac weyn ka dhacay 28 Febraayo 2020 (warbixin dheeraad ah).
Tani waxay ugu horreyntii sababtay kororka degdegga ah ee kiisaska laga diiwaangeliyey Talyaaniga, laakiin dhammaan dalalka kale ee Midowga Yurub/EEZ iyo UK waxay la kulmeen isbeddello la mid ah kororka cudurka COVID-19 (warbixin dheeraad ah).
Sawirka 2 wuxuu muujinayaa tirada guud ee COVID-19 ee wadamada Midowga Yurub/EEZ iyo UK marka loo eego tirada la midka ah ee Talyaaniga ee 31 Janaayo ilaa 15 Maarso 2020.
Sida laga soo xigtay xogtan, tirada guud ee kiisaska laga helay 15kii Maarso saacadii 8aad ee 15ka waddan ee kale ee Midowga Yurub/EEA iyo UK waxay la mid tahay tirada laga helay Talyaaniga qiyaastii 3 toddobaad ka hor.
Natiijooyinkayagu waxay muujinayaan koror deg deg ah oo ku yimid tirada kiisaska COVID-19 ee laga helay Midowga Yurub/Aagga Dhaqaalaha Yurub iyo UK.
Isbeddellada la arkay ee cudurka COVID-19 ee isku darka ah ayaa tilmaamaya in cudurku uu ku socdo xawaare isku mid ah dhammaan dalalka.
Taasina waa inkastoo ay jiraan marxalado kala duwan oo ka jira dalal kala duwan, kala duwanaansho ku yimaada jawaab celinta ay qaadaan hay'adaha caafimaadka dadweynaha ee dalalka, iyo laga yaabee in ay jiraan shuruudo kala duwan oo lagu aqoonsado kiisaska iyo xeerar kala duwan oo lagu doorto bukaanka baaritaanka COVID-19, oo ay ku jiraan baaritaanka "ku-dhafan".
Bilowgii Maarso 2020, dhakhaatiirta gobollada ay saameysay Talyaaniga ayaa soo sheegay in qiyaastii 10% bukaannada qaba COVID-19 ay u baahan yihiin daryeel degdeg ah, warbaahintu waxay sheegtay in isbitaalada iyo qaybaha daryeelka degdegga ah ee gobolladaas ay horey u buuxsameen.
Waqtigan xaadirka ah xogta ku saabsan soo gelitaanka bukaannada qaba COVID-19 ee isbitaalada iyo (ama) qaybaha daaweynta degdegga ah ee Midowga Yurub/EEZ waxaa laga heli karaa oo keliya 6% iyo 1% kiisaska siday u kala horreeyaan (macluumaadka lama soo bandhigin).
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, waa in si nidaamsan loo ururiyaa xogta si loo buuxiyo xogta la socdo ee la xiriirta tirada kiisaska iyo dhimashada.
Daraasad lagu sameeyay 2010-2011 ayaa lagu ogaaday in Yurub ay ku kala duwan tahay sariiraha qaybaha daryeelka degdegga ah iyo kuwa bukaanka ee degdega ah, waxaana laga helay 29.2 sariirood oo Jarmal ah ilaa 4.2 sariirood oo 100 000 qof ah oo Portugal ah.
Taas macnaheedu waa in dalal kale ay leeyihiin kheyraad ka badan ama ka yar Talyaaniga (12.5 sariirood oo ku yaal qaybaha daryeelka degdegga ah iyo qaybaha daryeelka degdegga ah ee 100,000 oo qof sanadkii 2010-2011).
Warbixinta lixaad ee la cusbooneysiiyay ee ECDC ee ku saabsan natiijooyinka qiimeynta khatarta COVID-19 waxay soo bandhigeysaa xaalado lagu daydo howlaha caafimaadka ee la xidhiidha qiimeynta bukaanka COVID-19 ee ku jira waddan kasta oo Midowga Yurub/EEA ah iyo UK, marka khatarta sariiraha la heli karo ee qaybaha daryeelka degdegga ah ay ka badan tahay 90%.
Maadaama xaaladaha hadda ay ku kala kooban yihiin gobollada Midowga Yurub/EEA iyo UK, isbitaalada iyo qaybaha daryeelka degdegga ahna ay caadi ahaan u adeegaan dadka ku nool gobol gaar ah, waxaa lagula talinayaa in la bixiyo macluumaadka xaaladaha iyo tirada sariiraha ee qaybaha daryeelka degdegga ah marka ay suurtagal tahay heerka 2aad ee Nomenclature of Territorial Units for Statistics (NUTS-2).
Khibrada Talyaaniga iyo isbeddellada hadda ka jira dalal kale ayaa muujinaya in EU/EEA iyo UK ay si dhakhso leh u sii kordhayaan cudurka faafa ee COVID-19.
Sidaa darteed, wadamada, isbitaalada iyo qaybaha daryeelka degdegga ah waa inay diyaar u yihiin xaaladda la xiriirka SARS-CoV-2, oo aan hoos u dhicin muddo dheer, iyo kororka tirada bukaannada qaba COVID-19 ee u baahan daryeel caafimaad iyo gaar ahaan daryeelka degdegga ah, sida tusaale ahaan laga arki karo gobollada ay saameysay Talyaaniga.
Sida lagu sheegay warbixintii ugu dambeysay ee ECDC ee ku saabsan natiijooyinka qiimeynta khatarta degdegga ah, habka degdegga ah, ka hortagga iyo dhammaystirka ah ee lagu xakameynayo faafitaanka SARS-COV-2 ayaa muhiim u ah, iyadoo la raacayo isbeddel ka yimid xakamaynta ilaa yareynta saameynta, maadaama la tixgelinayo kororka degdegga ah ee la saadaalinayo ee cudurrada, go'aan qaadayaasha iyo isbitaalada laga yaabo inaysan haysan waqti ku filan oo ay ku fikiraan, qaataan oo ay si habboon u hagaajin karaan jawaabtooda haddii tallaabooyinkaas aan horay loo qaadin.
Warbixinta qiimeynta khatarta ayaa sidoo kale ku taxay tallaabooyinka caafimaadka dadweynaha ee lagu yareynayo saameynta cudurka faafa.
Wadamada waxay haystaan waqti kooban oo ay ku xoojin karaan dadaalkooda xakamaynta si ay u yareeyaan faafitaanka SARS-CoV-2 iyo yareynta culeyska nidaamyada caafimaadka.
Haddii aan la samayn, nidaamyada caafimaadka ee dalalka kale ee Midowga Yurub/EEA waxay la kulmi doonaan dad badan oo u baahan daryeel degdeg ah maalmaha ama toddobaadyada soo socda.
Cudurka coronavirus ee 2019 (COVID-19), oo ay sababtay cudurka coronavirus ee neefsashada ee daran ee nooca 2aad (SARS-CoV-2), wuxuu ahaa musiibo aadanaha u ah: ilaa iyo hadda Shiinaha iyo dalalka kale ee adduunka waxaa ku dhintay in ka badan 3 000 oo qof, tirada dadka qaba cudurka ayaa kor u dhaaftay 80 000.
Sida fayraska SARS-CoV ee la midka ah ee sababay in kumanaan qof ay ku dhacaan cudurka neefsashada ee daran sanadkii 2003, SARS-CoV-2 waxaa laga yaabaa in laga qaado jiirka oo ay keento calaamado la mid ah iyadoo la adeegsanayo hab la mid ah.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, COVID-19 waxay leedahay heerka xanuunka ee ka hooseeya iyo heerka dhimashada ee ka hooseeya SARS, laakiin waa mid aad u faafa waxayna saameyneysaa dadka waayeelka ah inta badan marka loo eego dadka da'da yar, ragga iyo dumarka.
Marka laga hadlayo kororka degdegga ah ee wararka ku saabsan cudurka cusub, maqaalkani wuxuu bixiyaa aragti dhammaystiran oo ku saabsan cilmi-baarista si dhakhso leh u soo baxda.
Waxaan ka hadli doonnaa arrimaha aasaasiga ah ee cudurka faafa, sababaha, fayraska, cudurka lagu ogaado, lagu daaweeyo, la saadaaliyo iyo ka hortagga cudurka.
Inkastoo su'aalo badan ay weli jiraan oo aan la jawaabin, waxaan rajeyneynaa in dib u eegista ay caawin doonto fahamka iyo baabi'inta cudurka halista ah.
Ciida guga (Sannadka Cusub ee Shiinaha) ee 2020 oo ku dhacday Janaayo 25, waxay noqotay dhacdo aan horay loo arag oo aan la illoobi karin dhammaan dadka Shiinaha, kuwaas oo la sheegay inay guriga joogaan inta lagu jiro ciida iyo toddobaadyo badan kadib cudurka cusub ee fayraska.
Iyada oo la tixgelinayo isku midnimada sare ee coronavirus (CoV) ee sababay cudurka neefsashada ee daran ee daran (SARS) sanadkii 2003, Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka (WHO) ayaa 11kii Febraayo 2020 magacaabay virus-ka SARS-CoV-2, cudurka la socda  cudurka coronavirus 19 (COVID-19).
Cudurka ayaa ka bilaabmay magaalada Wuhan ee dalka Shiinaha, wuxuuna si dhakhso leh ugu faafay dalka oo dhan, kadibna wuxuu ku dhowaad 50 dal oo kale oo adduunka ah.
Sida laga soo xigtay 2da Maarso 2020, waxaa la xaqiijiyay in ka badan 80,000 oo kiis oo COVID-19, in ka badan 40,000 oo bukaan ayaa bogsaday, in ka badan 3,000 oo bukaan ayaa dhintay.
WHO waxay ka digtay in COVID-19 uu yahay "Cadowga ugu weyn ee bulshada" oo ay u badan tahay inuu ka khatar badan yahay argagixisada.
Sida laga soo xigtay PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), in ka yar laba bilood ayaa waxaa soo baxay in ka badan 200 oo daabacaad oo ku saabsan COVID-19, oo ay ku jiraan maqaallo ku saabsan fayrasyadda, cudurrada faafa, cilmiga cudurka, baaritaanka iyo daaweynta, laga bilaabo warbixintii ugu horreysay ee Janaayo 7, 2020, oo lagu ogaaday taxanaha fayraska ee laga soo saaray bukaanno badan.
Dib u eegistaani waxay isku daydaa in ay soo koobto natiijooyinka cilmi baarista ee ku saabsan mawduuc cusub oo si dhakhso leh u soo koraya.
Marka ay suurtagal tahay, waxaan isku dayi doonnaa inaan isbarbardhigno COVID-19 iyo SARS iyo cudurka kale ee coronavirus ee loo yaqaan 'Middle East Respiratory Syndrome' (MERS) oo ka dillaacay 2012.
Waxaanu sidoo kale ka wada hadli doonnaa xaqiiqooyinka la ogyahay ee ka hortagga iyo saadaalinta cudurka, iyo sidoo kale qaar ka mid ah arrimaha kale ee muhiimka ah.
Cudurka Corona waxaa loo tixgeliyaa cudurrada aan u dhiman karin dadka, waxayna sababaan qiyaastii 15% cudurrada neefsashada guud 4.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, qarnigan waxaan laba jeer la kulanay cudurrada aadanaha ee loo yaqaan 'coronavirus' ee cudurrada badan u keena, kuwaas oo ah cudurka 'coronavirus' ee cudurka neefsashada ee daran (SARS-CoV-2) iyo cudurka 'coronavirus' ee cudurka neefsashada ee Bariga Dhexe (MERS-CoV), kuwaas oo sababay cudurrada ugu horreeya ee Shiinaha sanadkii 2003 iyo Sacuudi Carabiya sanadkii 2012 siday u kala horreeyaan, isla markaana si dhakhso leh ugu faafay dalal kale oo badan oo leh heerar aad u daran oo cudurrada iyo dhimashada.
Sidaa darteed, COVID-19 ee hadda jirta waa cudurka saddexaad ee cudurka coronavirus ee taariikhda aadanaha.
