Isbedelka cusub ee HCoV: dib ugu noqoshada heerka eber
Kala duwanaanta fayraska 'coronavirus' ee jiirka ayaa fursado badan u abuureysa in ay soo baxaan HCoVs cusub.
Marka la eego, cudurka loo yaqaan 'bat coronaviruses' ayaa ah xididka hidde-wadaha ee HCoV.
