Wargeyska Talyaaniga ee La Stampa ayaa soo xigtay "ilaa iyo hadda ilo siyaasadeed oo heer sare ah" oo aan la sheegin oo sheegay in 80% gargaarka Ruushka uu ahaa "aan faa'iido lahayn ama aan waxtar u lahayn Talyaaniga".
Ilo wareedhu wuxuu ku eedeeyay Ruushka inuu doonayo inuu muujiyo aragti wanaagsan oo caalamiga ah heer geopolitical iyo diblomaasiyadeed.
