Mid ka mid ah baaritaannada ugu horeeya ee PCR waxaa lagu sameeyay xarunta caafimaadka ee Sharite, Berlin, bishii Janaayo ee sannadkii 2020 iyadoo la adeegsanayo falcelinta silsiladda ee polymerase ee waqtiga dhabta ah ee dib-u-qorista (rRT-PCR) waxayna aasaas u noqotay 250,000 oo xirmo oo ay markii dambe qaybisay Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka (WHO).
Bishii Janaayo 23, 2020, Boqortooyada Ingiriiska ayaa sidoo kale sameysay baaritaankeeda. Bishii Janaayo 28, 2020, shirkadda Koonfurta Kuuriya ee Kogenebiotech waxay sameysay qalab lagu ogaado SARS-CoV-2 oo ku saleysan heerka bukaanka PCR (PowerChek Coronavirus).
Waxay muujineysaa hiddaha E ee loo wadaago dhammaan fayrasyada beta-coronavirus iyo hiddaha RdRp ee loogu talagalay SARS-CoV-2. Shirkadda BGI Group ee Shiinaha ayaa noqotay shirkaddii ugu horreysay ee ay hesho oggolaanshaha Maamulka Dawooyinka Qaranka ee Shiinaha si ay u isticmaasho qalabka degdegga ah ee lagu ogaado SARS-CoV-2 oo ku saleysan PCR. Mareykanka Xarumaha Xakamaynta iyo Kahortagga Cudurrada (CDC) waxay ku faafiyaan International Reagent Resource guddigooda baaritaanka ee waqtiga dhabta ah ee RT-PCR (2019-Novel Coronavirus (2019-nCoV) Real-Time RT-PCR Diagnostic Panel) ee shaybaarada caafimaadka dadweynaha.
