Cilmi baaris badan ayaa muujineysa in xabagta warqadda ay ka caafimaad badan tahay qalabka gacanta lagu qalajiyo ee korontada lagu isticmaalo ee lagu rakibo musqusha badan.
Sanadkii 2008 Jaamacadda Westminster ee London ayaa sameysay daraasad ay maalgelisay simfoosinka Yurub ee soo saarista dharka waraaqaha iyo dharka dharka; waxa ay barashadu ku barbardhigtay heerka nadaafadda ee dharka dharka, qalabka gacmaha lagu qalajiyo hawada diiran iyo qalabka gacmaha hawada ee casriga ah.
