Cudurka neefsashada ee daran ee loo yaqaan 'Severe Acute Respiratory Coronavirus Syndrome 2' (SARS-CoV-2)  waa cudur cusub oo neefsashada oo daran oo loo yaqaan 'coronavirus respiratory syndrome' oo markii ugu horreysay laga helay saddex qof oo qaba cudurka sambabada ee ka mid ah dadka qaba cudurrada neefsashada ee daran ee laga helay Wuhan.
